# =============================================================================
# Unicodex Rust SDK — .gitignore
# =============================================================================
# 目的：当本 SDK 目录被 `git init` 初始化为独立子仓库时，避免把 Cargo 构建产物
#       与本地缓存提交进去。源码（src/、tests/、testdata/、Cargo.toml、
#       Cargo.lock、README.md、LICENSE）应当被追踪。
# Purpose: when this SDK directory is `git init`-ed as a standalone sub-repo,
#          keep Cargo build artifacts and local caches out of version control.
# =============================================================================

# Cargo/rustc 编译输出目录（构建产物，体积大、可重建）。
# Cargo/rustc compilation output directory (large, regenerable build artifacts).
/target/
target/

# rustc 增量编译缓存（若被配置到非默认位置）。
# Incremental compilation cache (when redirected outside target/).
**/*.rs.bk

# 后端 panic 时产生的核心转储。
# Core dumps produced on backend panics.
*.pdb

# 本地环境与编辑器杂项。
# Local environment and editor cruft.
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/
